      <title>印尼建筑商力宝因债券回购面临投资者考验</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/indonesian-builder-lippo-faces-investor-test-with-bond-buyback</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于借贷成本上升挤压了亚洲开发商的财务状况，印尼建筑商 PT Lippo Karawaci 回购美元债券的计划将成为周一的焦点。]]></description>
